Mapping it Out

City of Fairfax gets strategic about future of parks and recreation.

On a summer Sunday afternoon, several people huddle over a giant digital map of Van Dyck Park spread out across tables at the Sherwood Community Center, musing about future amenities at the City of Fairfax’s oldest and largest park, located just across the street.

Pride Connections - Episode 23
Pride Connections
Pride Connections - Episode 23
Episode Info

Episode 23:

On this episode of Pride Connections, host Melissa DaSilva sits down with Brynn TanneHill! Brynn graduated from the Naval Academy, earned her Naval Aviator wings and flew patrol aircrafts during her two deployments.

During this episode, you will learn more about Brynn’s transformation and how she is using her experience to inspire others and change the world as we know it for members of the LGBTQ community serving in the armed forces around the world.

This is an educational episode you won’t want to miss!

Mallow, Co. Cork Wedding DVDs

What a beautiful wedding of Marianela and Noel at the beautify Springfort Hall Country House near Mallow in Co. Cork. 

The couple had a civil ceremony on location at the hotel where family and friends gathered to witness the wonderful event.

They had their bridal and family shots on the grounds of this stunning hotel.

Dinner was served at 5.30pm followed by the speeches and the coupled and their guests partied the night away.
